  "abstract": "The 32-entry 1984 International Pearl Millet Ergot Nursery (IPMEN), eighth in tha series, was evaluated at 8 locations in India. Although no entry remained ergot-free at all locations, five entries had across-location maeans sverities of not more than 1% and the maximum of not more than 7% at any one location...",
